OL,6,FStuart Simons had cycled extensively
OL,7,Fabroad and throughout the UK, clocking
OL,8,Fup around an average of 7,500 miles
OL,9,Fevery year, but was killed just two
OL,10,Fmiles from his home.JMr Simons' wife,
OL,11,FClaire told a court: "It breaks my
OL,12,Fheart knowing that Stu will not see
OL,13,Fhis girls grow up, he will not be able
OL,14,Fto drive them to prom, to wave them
OL,15,Foff to college or proudly walk them
OL,16,Fdown the aisle and he will never meet
OL,17,Fhis grandchildren."JShe told how her
OL,18,Fhusband took part in charity cycle
OL,19,Frides in memory of their daughter
OL,20,FMartha Rose, who died in 2012 from a
OL,21,Fcongenital heart defect aged just four
OL,22,Fmonths.JDriver, David Parker, 67, of
OL,23,FTorrington Road, struck the rear of Mr
OL,24,FSimons' cycle on the A1077 at around
OL,25,F5.30am on October 7, 2022. He was
OL,26,Fjailed for 21 months and banned from
