OL,10,F24 perfect years.J"On the 7th of
OL,11,FOctober 2022 my world was ripped
OL,12,Fapart, changed forever, my future
OL,13,Fdestroyed. My girls were happily
OL,14,Fgetting ready for school that morning
OL,15,Fwhen the knock at the door came. Two
OL,16,Fpolice officers stood there and their
OL,17,Fwords still haunt me.J"I then had to
