OL,8,Fdecent, kind, loving family man has
OL,9,Fbeen taken away too soon and the
OL,10,Fimpact of that is indescribable."JMr
OL,11,FSimons' brother Damian said: "Words do
OL,12,Fnot scratch the surface of providing
OL,13,Fan insight in the full HD, surround-
OL,14,Fsound experience of grief and loss.
OL,15,FThe true experience hits much harder
OL,16,Fand is relentless, my head is always
OL,17,Ffull of questions which cannot be
