OL,6,FHe said Parker had a good driving
OL,7,Frecord over 32 years. The professional
OL,8,Fwelder is the sole carer for his ill
OL,9,Fwife, the defence barrister said.JHe
OL,10,Fsaid his client will never drive a car
OL,11,Fever again. Parker is a father of two
OL,12,Fand grandfather of four. References
OL,13,Fhanded to the judge spoke of his
OL,14,F"unassuming, good-hearted character
OL,15,Fwith strong moral principles."JJudge
OL,16,FRichard Woolfall said: "The factor
OL,17,Fthat makes this dangerous was that you
OL,18,Fhad at least 24 seconds to notice Mr
OL,19,FSimons. It is a long time."JHe said Mr
OL,20,FSimons was a vulnerable road user on
